### PWHL Scoreboard Data (HockeyTech API)
# This is the primary call used by the integration to fetch live scores and schedules.
GET https://lscluster.hockeytech.com/feed/index.php?feed=modulekit&view=scorebar&key=446521baf8c38984&client_code=pwhl&lang=en&fmt=json&numberofdaysback=1&numberofdaysahead=10
User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 11_6) AppleWebKit/605.1.15 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/15.0 Safari/605.1.15

### PWHL Team Roster
# Replace {{team_id}} with the numeric team ID (e.g., 3 for Montreal).
GET https://lscluster.hockeytech.com/feed/index.php?feed=modulekit&view=roster&key=446521baf8c38984&client_code=pwhl&lang=en&fmt=json&team_id=3
User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 11_6) AppleWebKit/605.1.15 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/15.0 Safari/605.1.15

### PWHL Team Information
# Replace {{team_id}} with the numeric team ID.
GET https://lscluster.hockeytech.com/feed/index.php?feed=modulekit&view=team_info&key=446521baf8c38984&client_code=pwhl&lang=en&fmt=json&team_id=3
User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 11_6) AppleWebKit/605.1.15 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/15.0 Safari/605.1.15

### PWHL Game Details (Boxscore)
# Replace {{game_id}} with the numeric game ID.
GET https://lscluster.hockeytech.com/feed/index.php?feed=modulekit&view=gamecenter&key=446521baf8c38984&client_code=pwhl&lang=en&fmt=json&game_id=326
User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 11_6) AppleWebKit/605.1.15 (KHTML, like Gecko) Version/15.0 Safari/605.1.15
